    <item>
      <title>不列颠哥伦比亚省在四年内获得第四个学分降级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/british-columbia-gets-fourth-credit-downgrade-in-four-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[不列颠哥伦比亚省的信用等级已被S＆amp; p全球评级降低到A+，因为在政府支出不断提高的同时，加拿大省的经济增长降低了移民和贸易不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/british-columbia-gets-fourth-credit-downgrade-in-four-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 21:03:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普征收10％全球关税，美国股票期货跌跌撞撞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/us-stocks-slide-as-economic-worries-flare-ahead-of-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统表示，美国将开始对其全球贸易伙伴征收10％的关税，美国股票的趋势急剧下降，数十个国家面临最大的贸易失衡的国家率高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/us-stocks-slide-as-economic-worries-flare-ahead-of-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 13:50:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在特朗普的关税上股票很晚的交易：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三晚些时候，在市场上，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）被称为美国长期繁荣的关键，在股权基准中降低了2％或以上的降低，而股票基准却在三天内集结了三天，希望该计划将不那么严厉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 22:27:39 GMT</pubDate>
